      "description": "# Bounce Defense \u2013 A Physics-Powered Tower Defense by Voodoo!\n\n**Every bounce is a blast!**\nStep into the most addictive physics-based **tower defense strategy game** where every ricochet matters. In **Bounce Defense**, you\u2019ll drop into a world of chaotic fun, clever positioning, and explosive chain reactions. Built by **Voodoo**, this game delivers the perfect blend of **easy-to-learn gameplay** and **deep tactical challenge** that fans love.\n\n## Think Fast. Bounce Smarter.\n\nEnemies are coming in endless waves\u2014and your only weapon is a bouncing ball that unleashes destruction wherever it goes. Place bouncers and weapons on a **tactical grid** to guide your ball, **trigger attacks**, and build unstoppable defenses. It\u2019s **tower defense meets pinball** in the most satisfying way possible.\n\n## Game Features\n\n**Physics-Based Strategy**\nUse bounce mechanics to chain together hits, ricochet around defenses, and take out entire waves with a single move.\n\n**Grid-Based Defense Building**\nPlace bouncer blocks, turrets, lasers, and explosive weapons to craft the perfect path of destruction.\n\n**Satisfying Chain Reactions**\nTrigger smart combos\u2014each weapon has unique cooldowns, effects, and timing. Master your setup for maximum mayhem.\n\n**Upgrade Everything**\nUnlock new weapons, improve damage, tweak bounce patterns, and push your strategy to the limit.\n\n**Endless Enemy Waves**\nFace off against increasingly tough enemy hordes. The longer you survive, the more intense the action becomes!\n\n**Neon Visuals + Explosive FX**\nBright, stylized visuals with screen-shaking blasts and smooth, satisfying destruction that feels amazing every time.\n\n## Built for Voodoo Fans\n\nIf you love **Voodoo\u2019s signature games**\u2014fast, fun, and deeply addictive\u2014**Bounce Defense** is your next obsession. Whether you\u2019re into **idle shooters**, **physics puzzles**, or **tower defense strategy**, this game hits all the right notes.\n\n## Why You\u2019ll Love It\n\nEasy to pick up, hard to master\nOffline-friendly gameplay\nQuick sessions with deep replayability\nGreat for fans of **Ball Blast**, **Pinball Tower Defense**, and **bounce puzzle games**\nNew content, upgrades, and weapons added regularly!\n\n# Download Bounce Defense Now!\n\nStart bouncing, blasting, and building your way through **bounce-fueled chaos**!\nOnly the smartest survivors will build the perfect battlefield and hold off the endless swarm.\n\n**Ready to bounce your way to victory?** Tap install and join the action now!\n\nPRIVACY POLICY:\n\nhttps://www.voodoo.io/privacy\n\n\n\nTERMS OF SERVICE:\n\nhttps://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/",
